[Aug-24]
Basin Reserve, Wellington
Waterside 6-2 Mosgiel
 [McCarthy 3, Sonny Ward, Walker, Longbottom - Sharpe, Rogers]
  
Waterside: Sid Ward, Bob Watts, Bob Bolton, Joe Calder, Fred Hazel, Phil
Traynor, Colin McCarthy, Tom Walker, Sonny Ward, Alf Longbottom, Toby
Janes. 
